 (3) Offcourse you can redirect the output of ProbeSCSI to a file and so store the
     info of your SCSI devices (and the devices of your friends), for later
     reference:

     Just Type:   ProbeSCSI scsi.device 1 >WORK:<yourfilename>

     If you have some output of exotic SCSI devices, like JukeBoxes, Scanners &
     Printers, mail them to me!  I don't have such devices to tryout...


